vote.title:
A public hearing to receive comments regarding an application for and an ordinance granting the renewal of Specific Use Permit No. 2119 for an alcoholic beverage establishment limited to a bar, lounge, or tavern on property zoned Planned Development District No. 808, on the south corner of Gaston Avenue and Tucker Street
Recommendation of Staff and CPC:  Approval for a three-year period, subject to conditions
Z189-369(CT)
